---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken & Rice Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: This Mexican-inspired dish comes together with minimal prep and a breezy cleanup, thanks to our oven-ready trays. You’ll season chicken with a blend of fajita-style spices and set atop saucy black beans. In a second tray, buttery Tex-Mex-spiced rice bakes alongside. Assemble your perfect bowls, top with sour cream and fresh cilantro, then toss the trays!
